# 🌍 GTCX Platform

> **Global Trust and Compliance eXchange** - Revolutionary blockchain-verified commodity global trade platform

## 🎯 Platform Overview

The GTCX Platform is a comprehensive ecosystem for transparent, compliant commodity trading. This unified monorepo structure contains three specialized applications that work together to create an end-to-end solution for the global commodity supply chain.

### 🌟 Key Innovation
- **GPS-Verified Sourcing**: Cryptographic proof of commodity origin location
- **Blockchain Compliance**: Immutable audit trails for regulatory requirements  
- **Digital Identity**: Cross-border KYC/AML verification
- **Professional Trading**: Institutional-grade commodity trading infrastructure

