### 🎯 Why Monorepo?

**✅ Development Benefits**
- **Shared Resources**: Common UI components, utilities, and types
- **Atomic Changes**: Single commit can update multiple applications
- **Consistent Tooling**: Unified linting, testing, and build processes
- **Cross-App Integration**: Easy data sharing between applications

**✅ Business Benefits**
- **Faster Development**: Reusable components and shared logic
- **Quality Assurance**: Consistent standards across all applications
- **Simplified Maintenance**: Single repository to manage and deploy
- **Unified Documentation**: Shared knowledge base for entire platform

## 📱 Application Suite

### 🗺️ GeoTag™ - GPS Commodity Verification
**Location:** `/apps/geotag/`

The flagship commodity verification application that ensures commodity sourcing compliance through GPS technology:

**🔍 Core Features**
- **GPS Location Verification**: Real-time cryptographic proof of commodity origin location
- **Photo Evidence Capture**: High-resolution images with metadata validation
- **Compliance Certificates**: Government-accepted documentation generation  
- **Blockchain Recording**: Immutable transaction and location logging

**👥 Target Users**: Commodity producers, cooperatives, compliance officers

---

### 🆔 TradePass™ - Digital Identity Platform  
**Location:** `/apps/tradepass/`

Comprehensive digital identity solution for cross-border commodity trading:

**🔍 Core Features**
- **Government ID Verification**: Multi-jurisdiction document validation
- **Biometric Authentication**: Facial recognition and fingerprint scanning
- **KYC/AML Compliance**: Automated know-your-customer workflows
- **Cross-Border Validation**: International identity verification protocols

**👥 Target Users**: Commodity traders, exporters, compliance officers, financial institutions

---

### 📊 TradeDesk™ - Professional Trading Platform
**Location:** `/apps/tradedesk/`

Institutional-grade trading platform for commodity professionals:

**🔍 Core Features**
- **Real-Time Market Data**: Live pricing and market analytics
- **Advanced Trading Tools**: Professional order management and execution
- **Portfolio Management**: Comprehensive asset tracking and reporting
- **Institutional Features**: High-volume trading and API integration

**👥 Target Users**: Professional commodity traders, investment firms, commodity exchanges

## 🚀 Quick Start Guide

### Prerequisites
- **Node.js**: 18.0+ 
- **npm**: 9.0+
- **Expo CLI**: Latest version
- **Git**: For version control

### 1️⃣ Repository Setup
```bash
# Clone the GTCX platform repository
git clone https://github.com/gtcx/gtcx-platform.git
cd gtcx

# Install all workspace dependencies
npm install

# Initialize development environment
npm run setup:dev
```

### 2️⃣ Development Commands

**🎯 Start All Applications**
```bash
npm run dev:all        # Starts all three apps simultaneously
```

**🎯 Individual Application Development**
```bash
npm run dev:geotag     # GeoTag™ on port 8081
npm run dev:tradepass  # TradePass™ on port 8082  
npm run dev:tradedesk  # TradeDesk™ on port 8083
```

**🎯 Quality Assurance**
```bash
npm run test:all       # Run all test suites
npm run lint:all       # Code quality checks
npm run type-check:all # TypeScript validation
npm run build:all      # Production builds
```

### 3️⃣ Mobile Development
```bash
# iOS Development
cd apps/geotag && npx expo start --ios
cd apps/tradepass && npx expo start --ios

# Android Development  
cd apps/geotag && npx expo start --android
cd apps/tradepass && npx expo start --android
```

